  "title": "Supplications for prostrating due to recitation of the Qur'an",
  "source": "Hisn al-Muslim 51",
  "arabic": "اللَّهُمَّ اكْتُبْ لِي بِهَا عِنْدَكَ أَجْراً وَضَعْ عَنِّي بِهَا وِزْراً وَاجْعَلْهَا لِي عِنْدَكَ ذُخْراً وَتَقَبَّلْهَا مِنِّي كَمَا تَقَبَّلْتَهَا مِنْ عَبْدِكَ دَاوُدَ",
  "meaning": "O Allah, record for me a reward for this (prostration), and remove from me a sin. Save it for me and accept it from me just as You had accepted it from Your servant Dawood.",
